			<section id="second" class="main">
				<header>
					<div class="container">
						<h2>The simple trick that makes this all work.</h2>
						<p>Big companies like Google and Microsoft are throwing lots of money and PhDs at the problem of fully automatic spoken translation. The quality of their results is good enough for alot of settings, but not for your amazing presentation. We focus on helping you craft a great experience so people will want to know what you have to say. All you need to do is prepare.</p>
					</div>
