					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="4u">
								<section>
									<h3>Three steps to get started</h3>
									<p>Your audience wants to be wowed. They want to be able to come, listen and engage with you. Some people take notes, but never get the chance to share them. Some people have questions that go unanswered. And sometimes you want constructive feedback on how to improve your message, but can't seem to get an honest answer. These challenges are multiplied when you present to a multilingual audience.</p>
									<p>It turns out that enhancing the multilingual experience with minimal effort also helps in every other aspect of communication. We designed SPF.IO to be straightforward to use. It requires some preparation to use effectively, but when you've done so, you give your audience a quality presentation and get the feedback that'll help you improve every time. Think of it like a flywheel. It takes work initially to get it spinning, but once it has enough momentum a little bit of effort can make a huge impact. SPF can help accelerate your message to multilingual audiences while increasing your effectiveness at the same time.</p>
									<footer>
										<a href="#third" class="button scrolly">How does SPF improve my presentations?</a>
									</footer>
								</section>
							</div>
							<div class="8u">
                <div class="row no-collapse">
                  <div class="6u"><header><h3>Your team will:</h3></header></div>
                  <div class="6u"><header><h3>Your audience will:</h3></header></div>
                </div>
								<div class="row no-collapse">
									<div class="6u"><a href="#" class="image fit"><img src="images/pic01.jpg" alt="" />1. Create</a></div>
									<div class="6u"><a href="#" class="image fit"><img src="images/pic02.jpg" alt="" />1. Connect</a></div>
								</div>
								<div class="row no-collapse">
